4.5.4 Comparison and evaluation
As a result, large amounts of information are processed automatically in the CZ. For example, data from USt audits, as well as key figures from balance sheets, profit and loss accounts are processed in the system.
The CZ is able to control the selection of risky cases on the basis of a wide range of information.
The same applies to the evaluation and management of USt audits in general.
In the CZ, the establishment of a special financial office for large companies is planned for 2012.
In Germany, financial management does not collect comparable amounts of data.
Accordingly, it is more difficult to carry out these tasks in the same way.
More emphasis is placed on the selection of individual cases in this area.
